<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Daily1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Daily,</orth> adj. 1) happening by day: <cit><quote>with nightly tears and d. heart-sore sighs,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.4.132" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. II, 4, 132</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) happening every day: <bibl n="shak. luc 649" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 649</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 1.1.60" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 1, 60</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 2.569" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 569</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.6.85" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 6, 85</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.2.15" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 2, 15</bibl> (Ff <emph>earnest</emph>). <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.68" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 68</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.68" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 68</bibl> <bibl n="shak. cor 4.7.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 7, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.1.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 1, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.1.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 1, 19</bibl> <emph>(he hath a d. beauty in his life).</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>